  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Clinic Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Position: Full time, contract </p><p>Looking for candidates who can work: 35-36 hour week with 2 evenings per week and Saturday morning with 1 weekday and Sunday off. </p><p>Our clinic is located in Bishan<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to walk-in patients and clinic enquiries</li><li>Manage front desk patient registration, answer phone queries and emails</li><li>Provide administrative support and scheduling appointments</li><li>Process prescription accurately and dispensing of medication to patients</li><li>Cashiering and process billing transactions under different government schemes and managed care programmes</li><li>Assist Doctor with procedures whenever necessary</li><li>Manage inventory and replenish of medicines and consumable items</li><li>Maintain a clean and organized clinic environment</li><li>Assist with procedures, phlebotomy</li><li>Assist with other ad hoc duties assigned by Doctor</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Singaporean or Permanent Resident</li><li>Minimum 3 years of relevant working experience in a healthcare or clinic work environment.</li><li>Proficient in English. Ability to speak Mandarin or dialect is a bonus as there are patients who do not speak English.</li><li>Good knowledge and experience on claims submissions (eg. Third Party Administrator Portal, Insurance Provider Portal, Mediclaim Portal etc) will be an added advantage</li><li>Excellent customer service and communication skills</li><li>Responsible, well-organized and proactive</li><li>Strong attention to detail and ability to maintain accurate records</li><li>Computer literacy</li><li>Remuneration will be adjusted based on experience and performance.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please send your updated resume to admin@goodhealthmedical.com.sg</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified for an interview.</p>",
